videos.headline: USC takes down Stanford to win final Pac-12 tournament title
videos.description: USC celebrates after beating top-seeded Stanford to win its first Pac-12 tournament championship since 2014.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (USC takes down Stanford to win final Pac-12 tournament title) 2024/03/10 ESHEET

videos.description: Cameron Brink drains a 3-pointer vs. USC in the first quarter.

videos.headline: Cameron Brink hits a jumper vs. USC
